{{Top|leg}}
An '''Ossus dueling lens''' was a type of [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] [[Focusing lens/Legends|focusing lens]] that was widely used at the [[Ossus/Legends|Ossus]] [[Jedi Enclave (Ossus)|Jedi Enclave]]. It was intended to create a highly focused blade for providing fine-tuned control over one's lightsaber.

